{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"42378ca7d0","title":"转发济南市委镇反工作报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b25fdf6eb","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":13,"articleId":"42378ca7d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"7c570090e3","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共济南市委1951年4月5日关于济南市4月1日夜对反革命分子实行大速捕的情况给山东分局的报告。大速捕后，济南市委组织大批干部深入群众宣传，多方收集了对这次镇反行动的反映。"}],"contents":[{"id":"08baad48cd","type":"title","text":"转发济南市委镇反工作报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0"},{"id":"7c570090e3","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，大中市委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0"},{"id":"35d740fd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"下面是济南市委关于镇反工作的报告，很好，请各大中市委注意研究，照此办理。我希望各大中市委均有一个报告给中央。现已收到北京、天津、青岛、济南、重庆、兰州等六处的报告和上海、南京、杭州三处的计划，均很好。请各未报告的大城市和中等城市，例如各省省城及汕头、梧州、衡州、宜昌、九江、安源、芜湖、无锡、苏州、宁波、厦门、石家庄、唐山这一类城市，均向中央做一个镇反工作的报告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0"},{"id":"5ccc66ae6e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0"},{"id":"7b2e7eb0b5","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0"}],"page":{"id":"6ee2dcaaef","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"42378ca7d0","start":231,"end":231}}}},"__N_SSG":true}